          <h2>Physical Characteristics</h2>
          <p>The Moon is a rocky, airless world with a surface shaped by billions of years of asteroid and meteoroid impacts. Its relatively small size and lack of geological activity mean it has remained largely unchanged for eons.</p>

          <div class="info-box glass">
            <h3>Moon Quick Facts</h3>
